```plantuml
@startuml miztiik_aws-real-time-use-cases
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Contributor

rectangle "GitHub Repository" as Repo {
  rectangle "README.md" as RootReadme
  rectangle "Use Case" as UseCase {
    rectangle "use-case/README.md" as UseCaseReadme
    rectangle "Images" as UseCaseImages
  }
  rectangle "templates/README.md" as TemplateReadme
  rectangle "templates/interview_topics.md" as InterviewTopics
  rectangle ".github/FUNDING.yml" as FundingFile
}

' ========== Connections ==========
Contributor --> Repo : Explore repository
Repo <--> RootReadme : Provide overview\nContribution guidelines

' Use Case interactions
Repo <--> UseCase : View specific use case details
UseCase <--> UseCaseReadme : Load problem statement\nsolutions and metadata
UseCase <--> UseCaseImages : Display related images

' Template interactions
Repo <--> TemplateReadme : Guide for new use case submissions
Repo <--> InterviewTopics : Access interview topics

' Funding interactions
Repo <--> FundingFile : View donation details
@enduml
```